9mobile just revamped its MiFi and Router offers! Known for its consistency in empowering customers with innovative solutions and packages, individuals and businesses especially those who are internet-dependent can now do more with affordable, bumper-size and superfast data with convenience. 9mobile Chief Commercial Officer, Stjepan Udovicic, emphasizes that the revamp is the company’s commitment to boosting individuals and businesses with superfast data.  “We are committed to the superior customer experience of our customers at 9mobile, especially as COVID-19 has altered the world of work. More people are working remotely nowadays; they will need affordable and superfast data to execute their tasks and stay connected with colleagues and business associates. “Our revamped MiFi and Router Offers will see our customers enjoying more for less. For instance, a customer gets 45GB instant sign-up free data bonus upon purchase of a 4G MiFi device in the first month for just N15,000”, Udovicic said. Now, individuals and businesses can get MiFi data bonuses of 5GB on data plan purchases from N2,000 to N4,000 and 10GB data bonuses on data plan purchases from N5,000 and above. The MiFi device can be connected to a cellular network to provide internet connection for up to ten devices and Routers can be connected to a cellular network to provide internet service for up to 30 devices. The routers also come with a one-off bonus of 20GB valid for 30 days.
Since 9mobile’s entrance into the Nigerian market over a decade ago, it continues to transform lives with consistent innovation and roll-out of solutions that help people achieve more.